title: User query: Plan description from client LLM
log: Find the five suppliers who generated the highest total revenue. Revenue is defined as l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) aggregated over all lineitems for each supplier. Return the supplier information together with the computed revenue. Output in textfile.

operations.table: (SELECT l_suppkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount FROM lineitem) as X

operations.udf: (r: org.apache.wayang.basic.data.Record) => { val sid = r.getField(0).asInstanceOf[Int]; val price = r.getField(1).asInstanceOf[Double]; val disc = r.getField(2).asInstanceOf[Double]; val rev = price * (1.0 - disc); (sid, rev) }

operations.table: (SELECT s_suppkey, s_name, s_address FROM supplier) as X

operations.udf: (r: org.apache.wayang.basic.data.Record) => { val sid = r.getField(0).asInstanceOf[Int]; val name = r.getField(1).toString; val addr = r.getField(2).toString; (sid, name, addr) }
(t: ((Int, Double), (Int, String, String))) => { val sid = t._1._1; val rev = t._1._2; val name = t._2._2; val addr = t._2._3; (sid, name, addr, rev) }

log.thoughts: Computed revenue per supplier by summing lineitem revenue, then joined with supplier details to return supplier info with revenue. Final result is sorted and written to text file as requested.

title: Class: PlanMapper Mapped plan finalized for execution

data.table: (SELECT l_suppkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount FROM (SELECT l_suppkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount FROM lineitem) as X) as X

data.udf: (r: org.apache.wayang.basic.data.Record) => { val sid = r.getField(0).asInstanceOf[Int]; val price = r.getField(1).asInstanceOf[Double]; val disc = r.getField(2).asInstanceOf[Double]; val rev = price * (1.0 - disc); (sid, rev) }

data.table: (SELECT s_suppkey, s_name, s_address FROM (SELECT s_suppkey, s_name, s_address FROM supplier) as X) as X

data.udf: (r: org.apache.wayang.basic.data.Record) => { val sid = r.getField(0).asInstanceOf[Int]; val name = r.getField(1).toString; val addr = r.getField(2).toString; (sid, name, addr) }
(t: ((Int, Double), (Int, String, String))) => { val sid = t._1._1; val rev = t._1._2; val name = t._2._2; val addr = t._2._3; (sid, name, addr, rev) }
